  <entry>
    <title>fcitx5安装配置</title>
    <link href="/2022/08/01/fcitx5%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <url>/2022/08/01/fcitx5%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="fcitx5安装配置"><a href="#fcitx5安装配置" class="headerlink" title="fcitx5安装配置"></a>fcitx5安装配置</h2><h3 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><p>安装fcitx5：  </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">sudo pacman -S fcitx5-im fcitx5-chinese-addons fcitx5-pinyin-moegirl fcitx5-pinyin-zhwiki<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>配置环境变量<br>新建文件 <code>~/.pam_environment</code>添加</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">GTK_IM_MODULE <span class="hljs-attribute">DEFAULT</span>=fcitx<br>QT_IM_MODULE  <span class="hljs-attribute">DEFAULT</span>=fcitx<br>XMODIFIERS    <span class="hljs-attribute">DEFAULT</span>=\@im=fcitx<br>INPUT_METHOD  <span class="hljs-attribute">DEFAULT</span>=fcitx<br>SDL_IM_MODULE <span class="hljs-attribute">DEFAULT</span>=fcitx<br>GLFW_IM_MODULE <span class="hljs-attribute">DEFAULT</span>=ibus<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启后完成</p><h3 id="美化"><a href="#美化" class="headerlink" title="美化"></a>美化</h3><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs nginx"><span class="hljs-attribute">yay</span> -S fcitx5-nord<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>到fcitx5设置-附加组件-经典用户界面-主题调整</p>]]></content>
    
    
